---
// Stats section component with metrics
---

<section
  class="py-24 py-5 md:py-10 lg:py-15 xl:py-30 2xl:py-40"
  style="background-color: #F9DDD8;"
>
  <div class="mx-auto px-4 max-w-28/32">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <!-- Subtitle -->

      <p
        class="text-sm md:text-md lg:text-lg xl:text-xl uppercase text-gray-600 mb-8"
        style="line-height: 110%; letter-spacing: 5px;"
      >
        REAL OUTCOMES
      </p>
      <div class="mx-auto md:max-w-17/32">
        <h2
          class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-5xl 2xl:text-7xl font-bold text-brand-dark"
          style="line-height: 120%; font-weight: var(--font-weight-black);"
        >
          Built. Shipped. Delivered. Because slick products mean nothing without
          measurable results.
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
      <!-- Stat 3: Faster Time-to-Impact -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <p
          class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl 2xl:text-6xl text-brand-orange mb-4 mx-auto pb-4"
        >
          <span class="font-black">40%</span>
          <span class="font-light whitespace-nowrap"
            >Faster
            <br />
            Speed-to-Impact</span
          >
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-md lg:text-lg xl:text-xl"
        >
          From concept to market, our AI-accelerated approach cuts product
          development time without compromising quality.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Stat 2: Reduction in Rework -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <p
          class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl 2xl:text-6xl text-brand-orange mb-4 mx-auto pb-4"
        >
          <span class="font-black">30%</span>
          <span class="font-light"
            >Cost
            <br />
            Savings</span
          >
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-md lg:text-lg xl:text-xl"
        >
          Our ai-enabled teams cost less than traditional teams without
          compromising on the quality and speed vital to success.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Stat 1: Client Retention -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <p
          class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl 2xl:text-6xl text-brand-orange mb-4 mx-auto pb-4"
        >
          <span class="font-black">78%</span>
          <span class="font-light"
            >Client
            <br />
            Retention</span
          >
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-md lg:text-lg xl:text-xl"
        >
          Our clients stay with us because we deliver consistent results that
          drive real business impact.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
